init_text: When you die, you appear in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you. You find out that they are your previous reincarnations, and soon you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You are a young man who has just died in a car accident.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You find out that you are in a cinema with a number of other people who look like you.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: You soon find out that you are all your previous reincarnations, and you all begin watching your next life on the big screen.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Will we just be stuck here in this cinema forever?
